' Logical → Implementation mappings
[Representatives Management API] --> [RepresentativesController]
[Representatives Management API] --> [RepresentativeService]
[Representatives Management API] --> [RepresentativeMapper]
[Representatives Management API] --> [IShippingAgentRepository]

[PLMS Database] --> [Entity Framework Core]
[Entity Framework Core] --> [PortContext]
[PortContext] --> [Representative]
[PortContext] --> [ShippingAgent]

[External IAM Provider] --> [ASP.NET Auth Middleware]
[Notification Services (Email/SMS)] --> [NotificationService]

' Data contracts / domain
[RepresentativesController] --> [CreateRepresentativeDTO]
[RepresentativesController] --> [UpdateRepresentativeDTO]
[RepresentativesController] --> [RepresentativeDTO]
[RepresentativeMapper] --> [Representative]
[ShippingAgent] --> [Representative]

